                ]
            ]
        },
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "At March 31, 2026 and December 31, 2025, we maintained sufficient liquidity to meet current and contingent funding obligations as modeled in our Liquidity Stress Tests.",
            "block_bbox": [
                627,
